Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with understanding the internal representations of Convolutional Neural Networks (CNNs) trained on objects. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes a clustering technique to extract information from the CNNs. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with understanding the internal representations of AI models. 
4. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is also possible as the paper deals with understanding the internal representations of neural networks. 
5. cs.CL (Computation and Language) is less likely but still possible as the paper deals with understanding the semantics of object parts in images.
